#
# Xg233ai custom instruction decode
#

%rs2  20:5
%rs1  15:5
%rd    7:5

&r    rd rs1 rs2  !extern

@r    .......  ..... ..... ... ..... .......  &r  %rs2 %rs1 %rd

dma      0000110  ..... ..... 110 ..... 1111011  @r
sort     0010110  ..... ..... 110 ..... 1111011  @r
crush    0100110  ..... ..... 110 ..... 1111011  @r
expand   0110110  ..... ..... 110 ..... 1111011  @r
